    {
      "type": "frame",
      "id": "S5hIj",
      "x": 7660,
      "y": 1104,
      "name": "Hype — Design Notes",
      "layout": "vertical",
      "gap": 20,
      "padding": 24,
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "note",
          "id": "pdIMl",
          "name": "Note: ANIMATION INTENTS",
          "width": 900,
          "height": 190,
          "content": "ANIMATION INTENTS\n• Countdown digits: upward blur/slide transition on each second change (Skiper UI number-flow). Geist Mono's fixed digit width prevents layout shift when digits change.\n• Timer card hover: 1px purple border + outer purple glow (0 8 32 #A855F740) + slight -4px lift, 200ms ease-out.\n• Category chip: spring scale on activation (0.96→1) + background fade.\n• Hero/detail glow streaks: slow 8–12s opacity pulse (0.25↔0.45), no parallax.\n• Primary button hover: gradient brightness +10%, glow expands."
        },
        {
          "type": "note",
          "id": "o5v9Vo",
          "name": "Note: CREATE FLOW",
          "width": 900,
          "height": 190,
          "content": "CREATE FLOW\n• Submit → POST /api/timers → redirect to /t/:slug with the returned slug.\n• Submit pending state: button label becomes 'Creating…' (disabled, reduced glow) until the response arrives.\n• On first visit after a successful create, the 'Copy link' button pulses its glow twice (nudges sharing).\n• On 'Copy link' click: button label becomes '✓ Copied' for 1.5s + toast appears below (fade+slide, gone after 2s).\n• Validation: title required, 1–80 chars; date+time must be in the future. Errors show inline under the field on submit attempt (see Error State variant). User enters local time; it is converted to UTC before sending."
        },
        {
          "type": "note",
          "id": "e6kuC",
          "name": "Note: STATES & DATA",
          "width": 900,
          "height": 190,
          "content": "STATES & DATA\n• Explore loading: 6 skeleton cards instead of the grid (surface-2 shimmer).\n• Detail loading: dimmed units with '--' values instead of the countdown.\n• Ended check and remaining time are computed with the serverNow offset; never show negative values.\n• Expired curated timers are excluded from the Explore grid (backend filters them).\n• Unknown slug → 404 screen (Hype — 404)."
        },
        {
          "type": "note",
          "id": "UhRl1",
          "name": "Note: RESPONSIVE (MOBILE)",
          "width": 900,
          "height": 190,
          "content": "RESPONSIVE (MOBILE NOTE)\n• Explore: single-column grid, hero countdown fontSize ~56, chips scroll horizontally, nav CTA collapses to '+ Create'.\n• Detail: countdown as a 2×2 grid (DAYS/HOURS on top, MINUTES/SECONDS below), fontSize ~72.\n• Create: form card full width, emoji palette 6 columns.\n• All touch targets ≥44px."
        }
      ]
    },
